{
  "texts": [
    "To map the current state of research on leveraging LLMs for AIG, our review is guided by the following research questions (RQs): RQ1: What are the most used LLMs for AIG, and how do their underlying architectures and features differ?",
    "RQ2: In what specific ways are LLMs most frequently used, and how do the LLMs' features influence their use in the AIG process?",
    "RQ3: What types of items were generated in the reviewed studies in terms of item type, subject domain, and language?",
    "Can LLMs generate valid, reliable, and high-quality items?",
    "The study search and selection process is displayed in Figure 1."
  ]
}